Papers discussed during 9/7/18 meeting

1.	Improving LDA topic models for microblogs via tweet pooling and automatic labeling
  Link: https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=2484166
  This paper discusses the importance of pooling tweets by their hashtags and making those a single document for the LDA model
 
2.	Twitter-Network Topic Model: A Full Bayesian Treatment for Social Network and Text Modeling
  Link: https://arxiv.org/abs/1609.06791
  This paper discusses the importance of a Twitter-Network model that employs the usage of a hierarchical Poisson Dirichlet Process to pool hashtags (idea from earlier paper repeated). Additionally, the paper puts importance on the significance of authors, as well as  a followers network
